creator: VanlifeLocation
descriptionHtml:
VanlifeLocation is your travel buddy for your trips with a van, camper, or rooftop tent.
We would love to accompany you on your journey through Europe and we want to show you the most beautiful places in nature for overnight stays.

You might be thinking to yourself right now: do we really need another app for campsite searching? We think you do!

Our goal at VanlifeLocation is to inspire you and to bring back the joy of finding new spots for your trip.
We are ambitioned to provide you with a clearly arranged app, that is easy to use and focuses on the users requirements.

In order to help you search for a spot we put value in beautiful pictures and good filtering options, next to the unique app design.

We don’t aim to be yet another database to recommend crowded campsites, concrete parking lots and disposal stations for caravans.
We love the vanlife lifestyle and the mission of our app is to also get you excited about it!

*GET AN OVERVIEW:
Spots which you will find on our map are mostly located in open nature and suitable for overnight stays.
If you like a spot you can save it to your “favorites”. You can do this either from the “detail view” or directly from the map.
In case you lose track you will find your last viewed spots on the dashboard.

*YOU ARE IN CONTROL:
Once uploaded, each spot can be edited by every user of the platform.
We trust the community and believe all users will benefit from this approach.
In case some information is incorrect, you can correct it at any time.

*OUR VALUES:
We care about nature and we would like you to leave the spots behind even cleaner than they were when you arrived.
Respect nature and treat the environment mindful at all times.
Please do not create a spot in areas where it is not allowed to stay.
We ask you to help other vanlifers with hints in case of wrong behaviour.


If you have questions or suggestions please do not hesitate to send us a message: info@vanlifelocation.com
We are happy to hear from you.

Thank you for being a part of our community!
Your VanlifeLocation Team.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: In our app, you can find free wild camping sites and soon there will be individual pitches from private hosts all over Europe as well. For now, you can visit our website vanlifelocation.com to book private pitches. You can make a binding booking for a pitch and transfer the overnight fee risk-free via our payment system. The range of pitches extends from simple parking spaces to pitches with sanitary facilities and panoramic views away from the camping hustle and bustle!
